messages.message: Thank you all for helping curate golden datasets! This is incredibly helpful to ensuring that we give Goldman a high quality set of programs. For example, I just used it to catch some date parsing issues with our Paychex_02 format.

If anyone has time, it will help speed us up as we are currently focused on building the Refiner programs; *Ultipro* and *Intuit_02* would benefit from having 10 documents annotated (currently we have 0)

After that, any amount of ADP documents we could get covered would be handy. Jessica did 10 which is perfect, but if people can pick up 5 documents here and there as the next few days progress that will also be quite helpful (we have about 40 total there; probably 30 ADP documents annotated total will be more than enough)
